                            <comment id="165537" author="adilger" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2016 22:08:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Chris, Richard isn&apos;t working in our group anymore, which is why there has not been any action here.  Rather than attaching documentation updates as patches to the Jira tickets, could you please push them directly to the &lt;tt&gt;doc/manual&lt;/tt&gt; project in Gerrit.  See &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Making+changes+to+the+Lustre+Manual+source&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Making+changes+to+the+Lustre+Manual+source&lt;/a&gt; for more details.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="115813" author="chunteraa" created="Tue, 19 May 2015 14:42:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Haven&apos;t seen an activity on this, will close in 30d if no further comments.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
